            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Ιαω <lb n="2"/>Αβρασαξ <lb n="3"/>πανεη αβλαν<lb break="no" n="4"/><surplus>ν</surplus>αθαναλβα <lb n="5"/>δαθε σαλυθεμ ετ υικτθωριαμ </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Tib</abbr><ex>erium</ex></expan> Clau<expan><ex>diu</ex><abbr>m</abbr></expan> Similem quem pe<lb break="no" n="2"/>perit Heren<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>ia</abbr></expan> Marcellina
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>δαθε σαλυθεμ ετ υικτθωριαμ ist als Latein &amp;quot;&amp;quot;date salutem et victoriam&amp;quot;&amp;quot; zu lesen.</p>
            </div>
